      "acceptanceCriteria": "Project requirements mandate that validation experiments use the same FDA generic pump geometry and blood analog fluid under the same five COU flow-speed combinations.",
      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump geometry with a blood analog fluid (glycerol-water mixture), but only three of the five COU operating points were experimentally tested. The two missing points are interpolated. Achieved level 3."
