      "acceptanceCriteria": "Project requirements mandate evaluation of the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model form against alternative models (e.g., strain-based, threshold-based) to bound model-form uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model was used; no alternative model form comparison was performed. Model-form uncertainty is unquantified. Critical epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
