      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Project requirements specify Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification on all hemolysis model input parameters including power-law coefficients and fluid rheology parameters.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but only fluid density and viscosity were varied; hemolysis model power-law coefficients (C, alpha, beta) were held at nominal values. Input uncertainty is substantially underestimated. Achieved level 2."
    },
