      "acceptanceCriteria": "Project requirements specify a minimum of n=5 replicate experimental runs per operating point with statistical characterization of inter-run variability.",
      "rationale": "Only n=2 replicate runs were performed per operating point. Statistical characterization of experimental variability is insufficient to support MRL 5 credibility requirements. Epistemic gap flagged."
