      "acceptanceCriteria": "Project requirements mandate formal equivalency mapping between experimental blood analog fluid properties and in-vivo blood rheology across the full COU operating range.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency analysis was performed between the glycerol-water blood analog and human blood under VAD shear conditions. Non-Newtonian effects at low shear rates are unaddressed. Epistemic gap flagged at MRL 5."
